<p>&amp; marked B1 (1 week). Met Budge Woods of Bourke who arrived from England today. Told me Barrett was a Corporal &amp; heard Forsythe killed. Went to concert last night in Salvation Army Hut. Wrote to Dick Luscombe, Uncle Charlie, Base Post Office &amp; home &amp; sent cossie picture to Maggie Fitz.<br/>6/3/18 Nice fine sunshine day.<br/>7/3/18 After tea went to concert given by R.G.A. Concert party. Warned to go away at any time.<br/>9/3/18 Got pack ready to leave the camp &amp; all lined up on parade ground &ndash; the marched to Medical Hut &amp; examined  by doctors. I was pulled out of the draft with three</p>
